dct_title_s: Atlas de Finlande, 1910, Texte 2 Population et Civilisation (Cartes Nos 24-55)
dct_alternative_sm: Atlas de Finlande, 1910, Texte 2 Population et Civilisation (Cartes Nos 24-55)
dct_description_sm: At head of title: Société de géographie de Finlande. Running title: Fennia, 30. This edition of the text differs from that which appeared as no. 30 in the series ""Fennia"" in that it was issued without series t.-p.; the atlas is the same as the one which accompanies the series edition (in French) Bibliographies at the end of the description of each map. Dimensions: illustrations, plates, maps (part double), diagrams ; 25 centimeters
